Devel-Hide version 0.00_02
==========================

Simple tool for developers which allow to hide
installed Perl modules. Used like this:

  perl -MDevel::Hide=Module/ToHide.pm script.pl


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires

  Test::More

for the testing part and recommends

  Test::Pod 1.18

also for testing - the POD part.

